<title>wǒ men zài zhè lǐ běn méi yǒu zhǎng cún de chéng 迦南1305</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men zài zhè lǐ běn méi yǒu zhǎng cún de chéng wǒ men zài zhè lǐ yě méi yǒu zhǎng cún de jiā
 nǎi shì xún qiú nà jiāng lái yǒng yuǎn de chéng hé jiā jiù shì zài tiān shàng yǒng yuǎn yǔ zhǔ tóng zhù
 shì shàng zuì fù yǒu de rén zhǔ kàn shì zuì pín qióng shì shàng yǒu zhǔ de pín qióng rén zhǔ kàn shì zuì fù zú
 nǐ shì fǒu yōng yǒu yé sū nǐ shì fǒu yōng yǒu yé sū nǐ cái néng bǎ wàn shì kàn rú fèn tǔ
 nǐ zài zhǔ de yǎn zhōng cái shì zuì yǒu fú</lyrics>
</song>